# Network impact

Using Office 365 may increase your organization’s Internet traffic. Email traffic with an Exchange hybrid deployment and directory synchronization activity will have the most impact on bandwidth, but some organizations may notice a general increase in Internet traffic after migrating users to Office 365. ([Source: Microsoft support](https://support.office.com/en-us/article/Network-and-migration-planning-for-Office-365-f5ee6c33-bcd7-4b0b-b0f8-dc1d9fb8d132?ui=en-US&rs=en-US&ad=US#estimatebandwidthrequirements))

This dashboard presents the total network impact generated by the most demanding Office 365 applications, namely Outlook, Skype for Business, OneDrive and Teams;
